    "descripcion_en": "Casa Comedia is the most important theater space in Colombia dedicated exclusively to humor and the comic arts. Located in a cozy venue in the south of Cali, in the Ciudad Jardín neighborhood, it has an intimate room with 150 seats, a stage of perfect proportions and a weekly program that includes stand-up comedy, theater of the absurd, clown, mime and musical comedy. Recognized by the Ministry of Culture as a concerted theater venue, Casa Comedia is the springboard for the best emerging Colombian comedians and has presented international figures of humor in Spanish as guests. Its small, open-access café-bar invites conversation and socialization before and after performances, generating a loyal community of regular spectators around the transformative power of laughter.",
